  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Action on  Children&apos;s Harmful Work in African Agriculture (ACHA).</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To improve the evidence base on the forms, drivers, and experiences of harmful children&#x2019;s work in African agri-food systems.  To identify, pilot, and assess the impacts of effective ways to reduce children&apos;s harmful work in the context of increasing integration of smallholder farmers and pastoralists into commercial agri-food systems.  To investigate the role of businesses in reducing children&#x2019;s harmful work, and provide a knowledge bank to support businesses and DFID programmeson related safeguarding issues.</narrative>
  </description>
